    "description": "WE-LHMI 4.7 uH shielded, metal-alloy (molded) SMT power inductor for SMPS output/energy-storage use. AEC-Q200 qualified, 125 degC Grade 1. This exemplar shows the two DISTINCT current ratings a power inductor carries: a MAGNETIC saturation limit (saturation_current, over the |dL/L| inductance-drop axis) and a THERMAL heating limit (rms_current, over the self-heating temperature-rise axis) - the usable continuous current is the lower of the two.",
